						               													<description>Magic of Legends is a co-operative adventure board game for 1-4 players.  &amp;#10;With no game master and only need streamlined rules, players take their heroes on a series of quests to find the secrets on the land of magic.  &amp;#10;On their way they'll face many challenges, including random maps, emergencies, dangerous traps, unlimited monsters and so on.  &amp;#10;In hero's turn, he or she can move, attack, trade, equip, heal or do nothing. Heroes need explore maps and find the story's goal point together.&amp;#10;In monster's turn, they will move to heroes and attack them.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;How to play&amp;#10;1.Select a set of story and your hero, then you can start an adventure quickly.&amp;#10;2.You will encounter the monsters in the adventure, or trigger a trap and so on, and also you will get treasures and other exciting rewards. Every time in your adventure, you'll encounter different maps, events, monsters, treasures, etc.&amp;#10;3.As the story progresses, you might encounter powerful Dark Lord.&amp;#10;4.Beat it, or escape, will bring you to a different ending.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Your goal is follow the story card's progress, and find the way to reach the winning goal.&amp;#10;There will have many different kinds of goals on the story cards. For example: you need take something, or reach to the special map tile, kill some monsters, etc. &amp;#10;When all heroes die, you will lose the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
